data.description:
This contemporary home is a hidden gem nestled in the serene woods of Collinsville, VA. The house boasts 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 luxurious bathrooms. The 2 full bathrooms and 1 half bath are perfect for accommodating guests.The house features 2 stunning decks that offer breathtaking views of the lush greenery in the backyard. The additional finished space in the basement has a private entrance and offers endless possibilities for entertainment and relaxation. Schools:
John Redd Smith Elementary School
Fieldale-Collinsville Middle School
Bassett High School
